## ✅ NHỮNG GÌ ĐÃ LÀM XONG (Theo thứ tự thời gian)

### Giai đoạn 1: Nền tảng
- [x] Setup Vite + React + TypeScript + TailwindCSS 4
- [x] Thiết kế UI Premium (glassmorphism, 3D effects, gradients)
- [x] Tạo Navbar responsive (desktop + mobile hamburger)
- [x] Footer với social links
- [x] Routing (React Router): `/`, `/heritage`, `/profile`

### Giai đoạn 2: Trang chủ
- [x] Hero section (animated gradient, floating cards)
- [x] Stats section (thống kê trực quan)
- [x] Environment monitoring (AQI, UV, Humidity, Wind)
- [x] Environment Chart (biểu đồ Recharts)
- [x] Health Advice cards (Modern + Traditional)
- [x] Traditional Remedy cards (25 bài thuốc dân gian)
- [x] Heritage Story section

### Giai đoạn 3: AI Chat
- [x] Tích hợp Gemini AI (multi-key rotation)
- [x] Multi-model fallback (flash-lite → flash → pro)
- [x] Heritage matching engine (keyword scoring algorithm)
- [x] System prompt tiếng Việt chuyên biệt
- [x] Medical safety disclaimer
- [x] Chat history persistence (localStorage)

### Giai đoạn 4: Authentication
- [x] Login/Register modal (animation, glassmorphism)
- [x] Google OAuth integration
- [x] Forgot Password: 3-step OTP flow (Email→OTP→Reset)
- [x] Password strength meter
- [x] SHA-256 password hashing (Web Crypto API)
- [x] Show/Hide password toggle

### Giai đoạn 5: Profile
- [x] Profile page (avatar, stats, achievements)
- [x] Avatar upload (base64 → localStorage)
- [x] Password change (SHA-256 hashed)
- [x] Security tab

### Giai đoạn 6: Polish & Optimization (Phiên hiện tại)
- [x] Local hóa 4 texture patterns → `public/textures/`
- [x] Thêm favicon.svg
- [x] Fix viewport accessibility (bỏ `user-scalable=no`)
- [x] Fix mobile menu hash navigation (Link → `<a>`)
- [x] Xóa unused imports (ChatWidget.tsx)
